PICOs.Population: Adults with advanced non-small cell lung cancer (NSCLC) with KRAS G12C mutation who have progressed after at least one prior systemic therapy, with an ECOG performance status of 0 or 1.
PICOs.Outcomes: Objective response rate, overall survival, progression-free survival, health-related quality of life.
